00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,000
Okay.

596
00:30:28,190 --> 00:30:28,880
Let's go.

597
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,830
Shiliu.

598
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:32,430
Shiliu.

599
00:30:33,470 --> 00:30:34,640
Shiliu.

600
00:30:36,310 --> 00:30:37,350
Shiliu.

601
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:38,800
Shiliu.

602
00:30:40,470 --> 00:30:41,640
Shiliu.

603
00:30:44,070 --> 00:30:45,310
What are you doing here?

604
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,400
Why are you hiding here?

605
00:30:50,070 --> 00:30:51,470
Why are you hiding?

606
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,350
I don't want to go to the welfare house.

607
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:54,950
I miss Liaoliao.

608
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:57,190
That's why you're hiding here?

609
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:00,760
Is this Liaoliao's room?

610
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:01,830
Yes.

611
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:06,880
Does He Huan want us to go to the welfare house?

612
00:31:06,950 --> 00:31:07,680
Yes.

613
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:11,640
If He Huan doesn't let you go,

614
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:12,880
