615
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:16,190
We all have to listen to him.

616
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:18,560
Mr. Shen.

617
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,310
Mr. Yang.

618
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:21,640
Liaoliao.

619
00:31:21,710 --> 00:31:24,160
Chi Liaoliao also listened to him?

620
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,310
Liaoliao

621
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:27,280
listened to him the most.

622
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:28,430
He Huan

623
00:31:28,430 --> 00:31:31,040
didn't like Liaoliao in colorful dresses

624
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:33,110
and she never wore those again.

625
00:31:33,830 --> 00:31:36,040
He also made her have cakes made from milk

626
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:37,760
