628
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:52,010
Let's go out and play.

629
00:31:52,520 --> 00:31:53,230
Go ahead.

630
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:50,070
Speak.

631
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,430
Who are you?

632
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,710
