635
00:32:57,430 --> 00:32:58,950
and I'm doomed to end miserably.

636
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,520
Live in my shadow?

637
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,000
What does that mean?

638
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,710
See?

639
00:33:57,880 --> 00:34:00,440
Zheng didn't just help out at the litigation booth.

640
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:01,840
He also bought me

641
00:34:02,080 --> 00:34:03,640
the belt I'd been longing

642
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:04,940
for years.

643
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:06,920
Thank you.

644
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,760
Black accessories suit you the best.

645
00:34:08,870 --> 00:34:10,040
Buyou.

646
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,190
How do you like my new outfit?

647
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,040
Sorry.

648
00:34:14,040 --> 00:34:14,810
