of your age should wear bright colors.

653
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:22,560
You look good.

654
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:24,280
Say thank you.

655
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,470
Thank you, Zheng.

656
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,280
Wen Yue.

657
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,360
- Look. - Yue.

658
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,470
Zheng gave me this belt.

659
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:29,840
Looks good, huh?

660
00:34:29,910 --> 00:34:30,670
Wen Yue.

661
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,560
Wen Yue, look.

662
00:34:31,560 --> 00:34:33,360
How do I look in yellow?

663
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,600
Zheng bought it for me.

664
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:35,190
What do you think?

665
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,280
- Your outfit... - Looks good.

666
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:37,360
Not bad.

667
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:39,280
Let me see.

668
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:42,230
Look.

669
00:34:43,390 --> 00:34:44,560
He's showing off to others.

670
00:34:44,560 --> 00:34:45,500
Yue, what's wrong?

671
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,670
Zheng.

672
00:34:48,430 --> 00:34:49,860
I know

673
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:52,250
