674
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,870
Now you're finally home.

675
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:56,930
I get it that you want to bond with them.

676
00:34:58,150 --> 00:34:58,760
Of course.

677
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:01,710
I've come here and caused them trouble.

678
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:02,710
Naturally,

679
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:03,710
I must offer something.

680
00:35:05,230 --> 00:35:05,870
After all,

681
00:35:06,630 --> 00:35:07,600
others wouldn't like me

682
00:35:09,430 --> 00:35:10,800
as much as you do.

683
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,520
I bet people in the welfare center

684
00:35:16,870 --> 00:35:18,430
like you very much too.

685
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:23,760
Of course.

686
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:25,760
Yeah?

687
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:31,020
[Suburb of East Capital]

688
00:35:33,710 --> 00:35:34,560
Mr. Zou.

689
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,230
What is this for?

690
00:35:37,150 --> 00:35:37,870
You are in charge

691
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,080
of the Ministry of Justice.

692
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:41,800
[Zou Mian, Manufacturing Bureau]
Please do me a favor.

693
00:35:55,950 --> 00:35:59,290
I have served the court all my life.

694
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:03,230
My youngest daughter Ziyin

695
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:05,360
matters more than anything to me.

696
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:08,040
I really can't bear to watch her

697
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:10,280
framed by villains

698
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,870
and suffer in jail

699
00:36:11,870 --> 00:36:14,080
due to wrongful conviction.

700
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:15,390
Mr. Liu.

701
00:36:15,670 --> 00:36:17,870
Please show mercy.

702
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,150
This case

703
00:36:23,430 --> 00:36:24,950
has reached His Majesty.

704
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,260
No one in East Capital

705
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,420
dares to meddle with this mess.

706
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,000
Mr. Liu.

707
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:33,970
Do you recognize this yellow silk cloth?

708
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:38,840
His Majesty once

709
00:36:39,190 --> 00:36:42,000
held my master's arm.

710
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:43,230
After that,

711
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,150
my master

712
00:36:44,390 --> 00:36:46,600
always kept this yellow silk cloth on his arm

713
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:47,630
and he's never bowed

714
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,870
to anyone ever since.

715
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,560
But today,

716
00:36:50,610 --> 00:36:52,080
my master bowed to you formally.

717
00:36:53,390 --> 00:36:55,230
It was like His Majesty was here.

718
00:36:55,710 --> 00:36:56,190
How is it

719
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,390
a "mess"?

720
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:07,080
Forgive me.

721
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:08,080
There's nothing I can do.

722
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,190
Mr. Zou, please

723
00:37:09,190 --> 00:37:10,190
seek help somewhere else.

724
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:30,150
Nothing went wrong at home, right?

725
00:37:30,950 --> 00:37:31,840
All staff on board

726
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,800
have signed irredeemable contracts.

727
00:37:34,390 --> 00:37:35,390
We also paid off

728
00:37:35,390 --> 00:37:36,600
everyone we've come across.

729
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,230
Please rest assured.

730
00:37:38,470 --> 00:37:39,520
Your secret visit here

731
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,230
is highly confidential.

732
00:37:41,910 --> 00:37:43,560
No one will know about it.

733
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:46,280
Still, a long night is fraught with dreams.

734
00:37:47,870 --> 00:37:49,430
I came in person

735
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:52,560
to get Ziyin out of trouble.

736
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:55,630
No matter how much it costs,

737
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:57,080
I must get her out.

738
00:37:59,470 --> 00:38:00,670
Go work on it.

739
00:38:17,910 --> 00:38:18,560
Father.

740
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:20,000
Have some tea.

741
00:38:21,470 --> 00:38:22,230
Okay.

742
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:28,150
Where is Zheng?

743
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,710
Where did that brat go again?

744
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,800
He's probably playing somewhere.

745
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:38,520
Father.

746
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:39,390
Mother.

747
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:40,710
What happened?

748
00:38:41,650 --> 00:38:42,910
How did you get hurt?

749
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:44,040
It was Goudan's fault.

750
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,470
He bought a new Mahoraga figure.

751
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,360
He was being petty

752
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:49,950
and wouldn't let me play.

753
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:51,910
Then...

754
00:38:52,040 --> 00:38:53,000
Then you fought?

755
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:55,280
No.

756
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:56,670
I got mad and ran away.

757
00:38:57,600 --> 00:38:59,600
Then I fell on the way home.

758
00:38:59,870 --> 00:39:01,040
You fell?

759
00:39:02,600 --> 00:39:03,470
He fell?

760
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:05,040
Go wash up.

761
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:05,950
Go ahead.

762
00:39:06,080 --> 00:39:06,600
Come on.

763
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:07,760
It's fine.

764
00:39:08,230 --> 00:39:09,600
- Silly kid. - It's just a figure.

765
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:11,000
I will make one for you.

766
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:11,800
Really?

767
00:39:12,870 --> 00:39:15,000
If you make a Mahoraga figure for me,

768
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,630
I swear I will keep it safe

769
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:18,120
and take it wherever I go.

770
00:39:18,180 --> 00:39:18,650
Okay.

771
00:39:19,020 --> 00:39:20,130
Deal.

772
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:00,390
Wen Yue.

773
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,320
I woke you up?

774
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:04,600
No.

775
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:07,910
Why are you staying up late?

776
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:10,580
I'm making a Mahoraga figure for Zheng.

777
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:13,290
A Mahoraga figure?

778
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:15,400
Why are you doing that?

779
00:40:18,520 --> 00:40:20,760
I made one for him when he was a kid.

780
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:23,710
He's been carrying it everywhere

781
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:25,770
all these years.

782
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,140
It's all worn out.

783
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:30,190
I'll make a new one for him.

784
00:40:31,120 --> 00:40:33,120
You two are close to each other.

785
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:34,910
He'll be happy

786
00:40:36,120 --> 00:40:37,630
no matter what you make for him.

787
00:40:38,390 --> 00:40:39,630
Wen Yue.

788
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,960
I want a Mahoraga figure too.

789
00:40:43,430 --> 00:40:45,530
Make one for me as well.

790
00:40:47,150 --> 00:40:49,520
Don't stay up too late.

791
00:41:18,150 --> 00:41:18,840
Zheng.

792
00:41:20,910 --> 00:41:21,760
Yue.

793
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,080
What are you doing?

794
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:26,150
I'm checking Mo's drawings.

795
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:28,670
No wonder you like Mo so much.

796
00:41:29,150 --> 00:41:29,910
Mo

797
00:41:29,910 --> 00:41:31,000
is really ingenious.

798
00:41:35,430 --> 00:41:36,230
This is for you.

799
00:41:59,230 --> 00:42:00,040
Zheng.

800
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:03,630
I will never forget

801
00:42:03,910 --> 00:42:05,410
our days at the boatyard

802
00:42:06,560 --> 00:42:08,600
as a family of four.

803
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:15,040
After our parents died,

804
00:42:15,870 --> 00:42:18,120
I've done things I'm not proud of

805
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,230
just to feed myself

806
00:42:20,710 --> 00:42:21,800
and survive.

807
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:26,520
But thankfully,

808
00:42:26,580 --> 00:42:28,620
we're reunited.

809
00:42:30,600 --> 00:42:33,470
Let's protect this new family

810
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:36,280
as if it's our original family.

811
00:42:36,470 --> 00:42:37,630
I have no other

812
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,670
biological family member

813
00:42:39,670 --> 00:42:41,360
in this world but you.

814
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:44,120
We have to live well

815
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,280
for our parents to rest in peace.

816
00:42:47,210 --> 00:42:47,810
Right?

817
00:42:52,910 --> 00:42:53,970
I'll do as you say.

