825
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:15,470
that making an oil paper umbrella

826
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:17,430
is a delicate matter.

827
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:19,280
It's divided into five steps.

828
00:43:19,710 --> 00:43:22,150
[Selecting Bamboo]
The first step is to select bamboo.

829
00:43:22,150 --> 00:43:24,870
There are strict requirements when it comes to selecting bamboo.

830
00:43:25,390 --> 00:43:27,000
[Making the skeleton]
Secondly, make the skeleton.

831
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:28,280
The bamboo is crafted,

832
00:43:28,430 --> 00:43:31,040
drilled, assembled, threaded,

833
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:33,520
and attached to a handle and an end tip into a skeleton.

834
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:35,760
[Applying the paper]
Thirdly, apply the paper.

835
00:43:35,760 --> 00:43:38,120
Paper is cut and glued onto the skeleton.

836
00:43:38,120 --> 00:43:40,870
It is trimmed, shaped, and exposed to sunlight.

837
00:43:40,950 --> 00:43:43,430
[Painting]
Fourthly, paint patterns.

838
00:43:43,430 --> 00:43:46,710
Paint patterns on the paper and dry it in the sun.

839
00:43:46,710 --> 00:43:49,800
[Applying oil]
Finally, apply cooked tung oil.

840
00:43:50,040 --> 00:43:52,390
Once the paper dries up, an umbrella is made.

841
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:55,280
Did my narration show you

842
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:57,120
